{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-07",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_07_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "G in the Air",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 4,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 727.392,
  "page_end_sec": 968.36,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.77,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 727.392,
      "end": 730.2,
      "text": "Spade blew cigarette smoke down the front of his vest and said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 731.2,
      "end": 731.96,
      "text": "That's probably right.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 732.36,
      "end": 734.34,
      "text": "He had only a few hundred in his pockets"
    },
    {
      "start": 734.34,
      "end": 735.8,
      "text": "when I frisked him this afternoon."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.06,
      "end": 738.88,
      "text": "When her eyes opened round and wide,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 738.96,
      "end": 739.54,
      "text": "he grinned."
    },
    {
      "start": 740.544,
      "end": 742.32,
      "text": "Eleventeen bent forward in his chair.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 742.96,
      "end": 745.58,
      "text": "He failed to keep eagerness from showing in his eyes and voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 746.54,
      "end": 748.72,
      "text": "I can be quite prepared to give you the money at,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 748.8,
      "end": 749.14,
      "text": "say,"
    },
    {
      "start": 749.28,
      "end": 750.74,
      "text": "half past ten in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.82,
      "end": 750.92,
      "text": "eh?"
    },
    {
      "start": 752.096,
      "end": 753.9,
      "text": "Bridget O'Shaughnessy smiled at him and said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 754.26,
      "end": 755.84,
      "text": "But I haven't got the falcon."
    },
    {
      "start": 756.928,
      "end": 759.28,
      "text": "Cairo's face was darkened by a flush of annoyance.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 759.66,
      "end": 762.06,
      "text": "He put an ugly hand on either arm of his chair,"
    },
    {
      "start": 762.78,
      "end": 763.34,
      "text": "holding his small,"
    },
    {
      "start": 763.44,
      "end": 765.46,
      "text": "boned body erect and stiff between them."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.2,
      "end": 767.32,
      "text": "His dark eyes were angry."
    },
    {
      "start": 767.94,
      "end": 768.94,
      "text": "He did not say anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 770.24,
      "end": 771.08,
      "text": "The girl made a mock,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 771.12,
      "end": 772.36,
      "text": "placatory face at him."
    },
    {
      "start": 773.42,
      "end": 774.74,
      "text": "I'll have it in a week at the most,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 774.76,
      "end": 774.92,
      "text": "though,"
    },
    {
      "start": 774.98,
      "end": 775.54,
      "text": "she said."
    },
    {
      "start": 776.72,
      "end": 777.26,
      "text": "Where is it?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 778.368,
      "end": 780.98,
      "text": "Cairo used politeness of mean to express skepticism.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 782.48,
      "end": 783.54,
      "text": "Where Floyd hid it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 784.32,
      "end": 785.02,
      "text": "Floyd?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 785.24,
      "end": 786.16,
      "text": "Thursby?"
    },
    {
      "start": 787.32,
      "end": 788.0,
      "text": "She nodded.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 789.26,
      "end": 790.56,
      "text": "And you know where that is,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 790.82,
      "end": 791.36,
      "text": "he asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 792.24,
      "end": 792.88,
      "text": "I think I do.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 794.26,
      "end": 795.96,
      "text": "Then why must we wait a week?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 797.28,
      "end": 798.42,
      "text": "Perhaps not a whole week.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 799.36,
      "end": 800.36,
      "text": "Whom are you buying it for,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 800.46,
      "end": 800.68,
      "text": "Joe?"
    },
    {
      "start": 802.016,
      "end": 803.2,
      "text": "Cairo raised his eyebrows.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 803.9,
      "end": 804.44,
      "text": "I told Mr."
    },
    {
      "start": 804.58,
      "end": 804.92,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 805.08,
      "end": 805.76,
      "text": "for its owner."
    },
    {
      "start": 807.072,
      "end": 808.8,
      "text": "Surprise illuminated the girl's face.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 809.58,
      "end": 810.58,
      "text": "So you went back to him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 811.21,
      "end": 811.86,
      "text": "Naturally,"
    },
    {
      "start": 811.9,
      "end": 812.4,
      "text": "I did."
    },
    {
      "start": 813.4,
      "end": 815.36,
      "text": "She laughed softly in her throat and said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 815.76,
      "end": 817.72,
      "text": "I should have liked to have seen that."
    },
    {
      "start": 818.848,
      "end": 819.7,
      "text": "Cairo shrugged.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 820.24,
      "end": 821.57,
      "text": "That was the logical development."
    },
    {
      "start": 822.56,
      "end": 825.0,
      "text": "He rubbed the back of one hand with the palm of the other.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 825.74,
      "end": 827.7,
      "text": "His upper lids came down to shade his eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 828.52,
      "end": 828.78,
      "text": "Why,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 829.0,
      "end": 831.26,
      "text": "if I in turn may ask a question,"
    },
    {
      "start": 831.74,
      "end": 833.66,
      "text": "are you willing to sell to me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 834.86,
      "end": 836.16,
      "text": "i'm afraid she said simply",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 836.72,
      "end": 840.94,
      "text": "after what happened to floyd that's why i haven't it now i'm afraid"
    },
    {
      "start": 840.94,
      "end": 843.0,
      "text": "to touch it except to turn it over to somebody"
    },
    {
      "start": 843.0,
      "end": 846.58,
      "text": "else right away spade propped on an elbow on"
    },
    {
      "start": 846.58,
      "end": 849.28,
      "text": "the sofa looked at and listened to them impartially"
    },
    {
      "start": 850.1,
      "end": 852.86,
      "text": "in the comfortable slackness of his body in the",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 852.98,
      "end": 854.3,
      "text": "easy stillness of his features"
    },
    {
      "start": 854.82,
      "end": 858.14,
      "text": "there was no indication of either curiosity or impatience"
    },
    {
      "start": 858.79,
      "end": 860.04,
      "text": "Exactly what,"
    },
    {
      "start": 860.26,
      "end": 862.0,
      "text": "Cairo asked in a low voice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 862.38,
      "end": 863.56,
      "text": "happened to Floyd?"
    },
    {
      "start": 864.9,
      "end": 866.62,
      "text": "The tip of Bridget O'Shaughnessy's right",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 866.62,
      "end": 869.28,
      "text": "forefinger traced a swift G in the air."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.24,
      "end": 870.68,
      "text": "Cairo said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 871.28,
      "end": 871.7,
      "text": "I see."
    },
    {
      "start": 872.64,
      "end": 874.36,
      "text": "But there was something doubting in his smile.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 875.38,
      "end": 875.94,
      "text": "Is he here?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 877.02,
      "end": 877.52,
      "text": "I don't know,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 877.64,
      "end": 878.67,
      "text": "she spoke impatiently."
    },
    {
      "start": 879.24,
      "end": 880.28,
      "text": "What difference does it make?"
    },
    {
      "start": 881.44,
      "end": 883.2,
      "text": "The doubt in Cairo's smile deepened.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 883.94,
      "end": 885.46,
      "text": "It might make a world of difference,"
    },
    {
      "start": 885.62,
      "end": 885.98,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 886.54,
      "end": 888.94,
      "text": "and rearranged his hands in his lap so that"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.02,
      "end": 890.16,
      "text": "intentionally or not,"
    },
    {
      "start": 890.38,
      "end": 892.6,
      "text": "a blunt forefinger pointed at Spade."
    },
    {
      "start": 892.9,
      "end": 895.12,
      "text": "The girl glanced at the pointing finger"
    },
    {
      "start": 895.38,
      "end": 897.26,
      "text": "and made an impatient motion with her head."
    },
    {
      "start": 897.94,
      "end": 898.24,
      "text": "Or me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 898.62,
      "end": 898.96,
      "text": "she said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 899.1,
      "end": 899.76,
      "text": "or you."
    },
    {
      "start": 900.94,
      "end": 901.54,
      "text": "Exactly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 901.68,
      "end": 902.56,
      "text": "and shall we add"
    },
    {
      "start": 902.64,
      "end": 904.04,
      "text": "more certainly the boy outside?"
    },
    {
      "start": 904.56,
      "end": 904.66,
      "text": "Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 905.62,
      "end": 906.72,
      "text": "she agreed and laughed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 907.02,
      "end": 907.52,
      "text": "Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 907.54,
      "end": 909.1,
      "text": "unless he's the one you had"
    },
    {
      "start": 909.24,
      "end": 910.16,
      "text": "in Constantinople."
    },
    {
      "start": 910.32,
      "end": 912.8,
      "text": "Sudden blood mottled Cairo's face."
    },
    {
      "start": 912.96,
      "end": 913.68,
      "text": "In a shrill,"
    },
    {
      "start": 913.68,
      "end": 914.32,
      "text": "enraged voice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 914.46,
      "end": 914.84,
      "text": "he cried,"
    },
    {
      "start": 915.26,
      "end": 916.56,
      "text": "the one you couldn't make."
    },
    {
      "start": 917.92,
      "end": 919.84,
      "text": "Bridget O'Shaughnessy jumped up from her chair.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 920.04,
      "end": 921.22,
      "text": "Her lower lip was"
    },
    {
      "start": 921.3,
      "end": 922.1,
      "text": "between her teeth."
    },
    {
      "start": 922.36,
      "end": 925.54,
      "text": "Her eyes were dark and wide and a tense white face."
    },
    {
      "start": 926.22,
      "end": 927.26,
      "text": "She took two quick steps"
    },
    {
      "start": 927.42,
      "end": 928.14,
      "text": "toward Cairo."
    },
    {
      "start": 928.28,
      "end": 929.48,
      "text": "He started to rise."
    },
    {
      "start": 929.72,
      "end": 932.94,
      "text": "Her right hand went out and cracked sharply against his cheek,"
    },
    {
      "start": 933.56,
      "end": 935.28,
      "text": "leaving the imprint of fingers there."
    },
    {
      "start": 936.224,
      "end": 937.86,
      "text": "Cairo grunted and slapped her cheek,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 938.04,
      "end": 939.3,
      "text": "staggering her sideways,"
    },
    {
      "start": 940.22,
      "end": 942.42,
      "text": "bringing from her mouth a brief muffled scream.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 943.54,
      "end": 944.06,
      "text": "Spade,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 944.2,
      "end": 945.08,
      "text": "wooden of face,"
    },
    {
      "start": 945.48,
      "end": 947.54,
      "text": "was up from the sofa and close to them by then."
    },
    {
      "start": 948.32,
      "end": 950.18,
      "text": "He caught Cairo by the throat and shook him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 950.976,
      "end": 953.04,
      "text": "Cairo gurgled and put a hand inside his coat.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 953.824,
      "end": 955.48,
      "text": "Spade grasped the Levantine's wrist,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 956.0,
      "end": 957.14,
      "text": "wrenched it away from the coat,"
    },
    {
      "start": 957.26,
      "end": 959.0,
      "text": "forced it straight out to the side,"
    },
    {
      "start": 959.18,
      "end": 960.98,
      "text": "and twisted it until the clumsy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 961.12,
      "end": 962.28,
      "text": "flaccid fingers opened"
    },
    {
      "start": 962.68,
      "end": 965.16,
      "text": "to let the black pistol fall down on the rug."
    },
    {
      "start": 966.08,
      "end": 967.18,
      "text": "Bridget O'Shaughnessy quickly",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 967.7,
      "end": 968.36,
      "text": "picked up the pistol."
    }
  ]
}